{"tid":1124421,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"求片 不甘被分手！臉書散布性愛影片　嫩妹怒告超渣前男友","createTime":"2019-04-25T04:35:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-25T05:32:08.000Z","uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"8b1cabc9337406c968ca9f82f920407f1312ac8d","tid":1124421,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T04:35:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">台南</span>市1名陳姓女子，先前接獲友人告知，指出LINE群組瘋傳性愛影片，其中一段命名為「寶貝寶貝好想要」影片，女主角與陳女極為相似，友人好奇詢問：這個人不是妳嗎？ 」，陳女點開連結一看，女主角果然是自己，令她既震驚又氣憤，隨即對石姓前男友提出告訴；台南地院依散布猥褻影像罪判石男4月徒刑，全案仍可上訴。<br />\n<br />\n檢警調查，石男與陳女原是男女朋友，後來因個性不合而分手；石男竟心生報復之意，先以暱稱登入臉書後，再上傳兩人共同拍攝的性愛影片，並以「寶貝寶貝好想要」為標題，石男還將影片狀態設為公開，提供不特定人士觀看，甚至傳送臉書網址給朋友，藉以讓影片廣為流傳。<br />\n<br />\n孰料，陳女友人收到連結後點開一看，赫然發現影片女主角竟是陳女，嚇得趕緊通知對方；陳女獲悉後怒不可遏，立刻翻拍影片做為證據，並與石男大吵一架，進而要求對方將影片下架，再前往警局提出告訴。<br />\n<br />\n石男應訊時坦承犯行，法官認為，石男與陳女曾是男女朋友關係，犯行不但侵害對方隱私甚鉅，而且有害社會善良風俗，迄今仍未與陳女達成和解，遂依散布猥褻影像罪判石男4月徒刑，得易科罰金，全案仍可上訴。<br />\n<br />\n求片<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"054015be7e1fd34dac722e7f9af134c059789d5a","tid":1124421,"uid":163937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T04:42:09.000Z","msg":"片呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2237df68599c633b78e41ebd2c9e7af768417734","tid":1124421,"uid":236904,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T04:43:41.000Z","msg":"網絡荒島 不服來片"},{"pid":"354c42940d10a4a374d154fb3cd51f0f1a92591e","tid":1124421,"uid":108236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T04:55:57.000Z","msg":"陳女友人有冇屌過陳女？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf34a08600f848c237aface535ac8f995ff291e2","tid":1124421,"uid":119695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T05:05:17.000Z","msg":"這是不對的"},{"pid":"3c7b024a48ddeb7ca678fcdfce7471944686f795","tid":1124421,"uid":164461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T05:10:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3d4992d114ff77177113172acc4cf9baaa9d0c4b","tid":1124421,"uid":217275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T05:12:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60727444519315c7e5e568493752fab4100e3fd0","tid":1124421,"uid":154255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T05:23:24.000Z","msg":"台灣垃圾作出黎既新聞<br />\n撚有片咩"},{"pid":"6c927a781fcaccbb7d5f7b478de1a834a64a9e2b","tid":1124421,"uid":51532,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T05:25:19.000Z","msg":"xhamster有，唔敢貼link，怕比人告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a533fcd5c1886a8de9fed930b339c07a4dc034c","tid":1124421,"uid":148874,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T05:26:56.000Z","msg":"唔奢望有片 圖都比張黎睇下啦大佬"},{"pid":"ae0e6bcd4df7d1566f15ef1350e019ec21e772d8","tid":1124421,"uid":65194,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6c927a781fcaccbb7d5f7b478de1a834a64a9e2b","tid":1124421,"uid":51532,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T05:25:19.000Z","msg":"xhamster有，唔敢貼link，怕比人告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T05:27:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df511608bf98f668386abf4d4a8c33365ee5b4db","tid":1124421,"uid":189528,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6c927a781fcaccbb7d5f7b478de1a834a64a9e2b","tid":1124421,"uid":51532,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T05:25:19.000Z","msg"